{"tid":840882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬爾代夫前總統：沒有一個合作項目商業上行得通 口交部：不是個別人可以抺黑","createTime":"2018-09-29T06:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T10:45:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bc405c9c2e31663042fb6a780c596ce813fa23","tid":840882,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"星島環球網消息：據報道，馬爾代夫前總統納希德接受印度媒體采訪稱，沒有一個中馬之間的項目在商業上行得通。中國外交部發言人耿爽在昨天（26日）的例行記者會上表示，中馬合作是否行得通、是否給兩國帶來利益，最終發言權在兩國人民，不是個別人可以抹黑的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示，對個別人總是發表這樣不負責任的言論深表遺憾和不解。中馬合作建立在平等自願、互利共贏基礎上，嚴格遵循市場規則和法律法規。如果有個別勢力出於政治目的任意損害中國利益，中方將堅決予以反對，堅決保護中資企業合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1881591&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1881591%26target%3D2&d=UAq61%2F6nKr4VVEwOI5rON0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e140ff9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1881591%26target%3D2&h=e145704f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1881591&amp;target=2</a>"},{"pid":"4be5f0bbb35377d75036bb201cd194a755368733","tid":840882,"uid":37528,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:04:06.000Z","msg":"口交部最近都幾多撚含 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e83abbb3071fb4964eb7f8e873262777b20e95","tid":840882,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"連一個親中既前總統都反共保平安<br />\n唔知現任總統點諗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d901c0af96a0932d4f14383263de234d8f9c693b","tid":840882,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse